    "Related WorkThis section reviews the literature in three primary areas relevant to the integration of a PIL in the Mistral LLM for enhanced information retrieval accuracy.",
    "These areas encompass advancements in LLMs, the challenges of information retrieval accuracy in these models, and the development and application of probabilistic inference in AI systems.",
    "Advancements in Large Language ModelsThe evolution of LLMs has been marked by several significant milestones.",
    "Initial models showcased the ability to generate text based on limited context, gradually evolving to more sophisticated systems capable of engaging in dialogue and answering complex queries [11][12][13].",
    "Subsequent developments saw LLMs being trained on increasingly diverse and expansive datasets, which enhanced their contextual understanding and response generation capabilities [11,[14][15][16]."
